  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示主分支和特性分支的开发情况。主分支上有几个关键提交，同时我们切了一个feature分支并行开发，最后要能看到两条线的合并关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main branch",
        "feature branch",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那feature分支的创建时机是在主分支的第一次提交之后吗？还有，两条分支各自的提交数量大概是怎样的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch creation point",
        "commit count"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，主分支先有一个初始提交a，然后切出feature分支。之后主分支继续有b、c、d三个提交，feature分支上有f、g两个提交。暂时先不画合并，展示并行状态就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit a",
        "commit b",
        "commit c",
        "commit d",
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把结构搭好了。主分支从a开始，然后切到feature分支，同时主分支继续走。我设置了一下显示参数，让分支名称和提交标签都能清晰展示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "showBranches",
        "showCommitLabel",
        "branch feature order: 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我看一下顺序——feature分支是在checkout main之后才切出来的吗？还是从a直接切的？我想确保分支创建的时机准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "branch feature"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是从a直接切的。流程是：commit a → branch feature → checkout main → commit b。这样feature就停在a的位置，main继续往前走。需要我调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit a",
        "branch feature",
        "checkout main",
        "commit b"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没问题，这样是对的。另外feature分支上的两个提交f和g，是在checkout feature之后连续做的，然后切回main做c和d。整个流程要体现出两次checkout的切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout feature",
        "commit f",
        "commit g",
        "checkout main",
        "commit c",
        "commit d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。现在图上能清楚看到：main线有a、b、c、d四个提交，feature线从a分出后有f、g两个提交，两次checkout切换点也都标出来了。分支显示和提交标签都开着，整体结构应该符合你的需求。",
